Puppet module: skel

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages skel software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include skel              # Install and run skel with standard configurations.
include skel::disable     # Disable skel service.
include skel::disableboot # Disable skel service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include skel::absent      # Remove skel package.

DEPENDENCIES:
